h a wicked man","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"April 3, 2013","format":false,"excerpt":"Abu Huraira reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cVerily, no one will enter Paradise but a soul submissive to Allah, yet Allah may support this religion by the hands of a wicked man.\u201d Source: S\u0323ah\u0323i\u0304h\u0323 al-Bukha\u0304ri\u0304 3062, S\u0323ah\u0323i\u0304h\u0323 Muslim 111 Grade: Muttafaqun Alayhi (authenticity\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Sin \u0627\u0644\u0625\u062b\u0645&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Sin \u0627\u0644\u0625\u062b\u0645","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/sin-al-ithm\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":3855,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2012\/07\/27\/love-surah-ikhlaas-jannah\/","url_meta":{"origin":17166,"position":3},"title":"Hadith on Quran: Love for Surat al-Ikhlas leads to Paradise","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"July 27, 2012","format":false,"excerpt":"Anas ibn Malik reported: A man said, \u201cO Messenger of Allah, I love this chapter, 'Say: He is Allah, the One,'\" (112:1). The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cYour love for it will admit\u00a0you into Paradise.\u201d Source: S\u0323ah\u0323i\u0304h\u0323 al-Bukha\u0304ri\u0304 774 Grade:\u00a0Sahih\u00a0(authentic) according to\u00a0Al-Bukhari \u0639\u064e\u0646\u0652 \u0623\u064e\u0646\u064e\u0633\u064d\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/righteousness-al-birr\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":7803,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2012\/10\/05\/suicide-kill-himself-jannah\/","url_meta":{"origin":17166,"position":4},"title":"Hadith on Suicide: Man